net.proteusframework.core.hibernate.model

Class AbstractEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.core.hibernate.model.AbstractEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Entity<Long>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractNamedEntity

    public abstract class AbstractEntity
extends Object
implements Entity<Long>
    A convenience base class for implementing Entitys with Long ids and adds introspection of equals and hashcode. This is only used for convenience, and should always be maintained as transparent to persistence code in case a subclass needs to be refactored to not use this class.
    Author:
    Kevin Beaty (kbeaty@i2rd.com)
